data.description: You will love this home from the top to the bottom. Step into your formal living/dining room with nice wood laminate flooring which flows through out the downstairs. You have a great eat in kitchen that opens into the family room. Lots of windows that will bring the outside in. Uniquely painted which just adds character to the rooms. Upstairs primary bedroom is huge and will accommodate an exercise area, reading area really anything you might want to put in the bedroom. One of the bedrooms has the same wood laminate flooring as the downstairs. New roof 2023, A/C is about 5 years old, and a brand new water heater. Recent gas stove makes the kitchen really shine. Gas log fireplace with the gas cooking will keep your downstairs nice and toasty even in a hard freeze when electricity is out. Carpeting needs to be replace and some minor TLC, seller will take those things into consideration with accepted offer. Hurry won't last long.
